    <datafield tag="520" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
      <subfield code="a">Collection of works, mostly selections from larger works, in Arabic and Persian, on Arabic grammar; copied in the same hand. A table of contents was written in at the front (f. 1r). The last three works are in Persian, of those, the two shorter works (5, 6) are in the form of questions and answers.</subfield>
    </datafield>
    <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
